<p style="text-align: center;"><em>If you are a professor of journalism/communications or scholar of news media at a college or university in the United States, <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf9tbDVqvi8-0a2eED4j4cYHKJAJ-bIPSRZRrDEaIQCWEH8jA/viewform" class="external" target="_blank">you can add your name to this letter, here</a>.</em></p>
										
																				
																		
										<div class="post_wrapper author">
											<div id="about_the_author">
